{"tid":2083680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"封整條彌敦道 辱罵市民「弱智」  靜默有罪警噴椒濫捕53人","createTime":"2020-06-29T02:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T02:18:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06f9ae06a54ce0a621475ea34feffd6833907881","tid":2083680,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:18:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/O7VAY764MGHQ5I74W47Y2ZIDFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FO7VAY764MGHQ5I74W47Y2ZIDFM%2F&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=df763e56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200629%2FO7VAY764MGHQ5I74W47Y2ZIDFM%2F&h=7c9aa144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200629/O7VAY764MGHQ5I74W47Y2ZIDFM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n封整條彌敦道 辱罵市民「弱智」 <br />\n靜默有罪警噴椒濫捕53人<br />\n<br />\n【惡法臨城】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法最快明日在北京通過，網民爭取最後反抗機會，發起「6.28靜默遊行」，於佐敦遊行至旺角。和平遊行再遭警方打壓，警員辱罵市民「儍仔」、「弱智」，又肆意噴胡椒噴霧，更以涉嫌非法集結濫捕市民。整日行動至少拘捕53人，包括兩名區議員及十名未成年人士。區議員質疑，警方目的旨在國安法生效前製造寒蟬效應。<br />\n<br />\n記者：廖承志 李詠希 張雅婷<br />\n<br />\n遊行昨午3時開始，警方早在下午2時後在佐敦裕華國貨外重兵佈防，站內亦有便衣探員駐守。下午3時，隊伍開始出發，有人舉起「五大訴求 缺一不可」手勢，亦有人高呼「7.1遊行見！」惟有防暴警冷笑回應：「7.1邊度會有人上街呀儍仔！」<br />\n<br />\n遊行開始六分鐘後，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n軍裝警員挑釁說：「趕時間就搭的士，唔好搭巴士！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9sgLUwoQ2SPtXFfLdpnkmf2hcxc=/1020x624/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2QZOXG3EYOYRVF7MR42RPDBONA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9sgLUwoQ2SPtXFfLdpnkmf2hcxc%3D%2F1020x624%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2QZOXG3EYOYRVF7MR42RPDBONA.gif&h=4d216504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方昨在旺角鬧市拘捕53人，包括兩名區議員及多名義務急救員。朱永倫攝<br />\n推撞記者 阻拍行動呼號<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：跟蹤13日 四神秘人監視黎宅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍抵達咸美頓街時，傳媒聯絡<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n。有市民無法離開，反遭警員嘲笑「係咪弱智」、「要人扶住先識行」。<br />\n<br />\n兆萬中心外，一群防暴警員拉起封鎖線。有目擊者指，一名警員疑失重心跌倒，旁邊的警員見狀大為緊張，沒有警告下向記者及市民施放胡椒噴劑，導致多人中椒不適。其後警方舉起藍旗，指稱行人路上記者及市民正參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「表達自由嘅空氣都冇」<br />\n<br />\n下午5時50分，警方於彌敦<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n往紅磡警署，徐子見其後疑因血糖過低，需送院。<br />\n<br />\n協助被捕人士的油尖旺區議<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，令市民行街、表達自由嘅空氣都冇，我哋十分之感到憤怒。」<br />\n<br />\n立法<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n，「市民冇任何口號、冇任何banner，總之到任何時間，佢就撈魚咁一圍，話呢五十幾個係啦！」他不相信最終會檢控，純粹為交差。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fX7mOKwnGf7fp-_T1Ypvbj0CUUg=/711x627/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AHYW5FF3ASRJLAB7Y6P77JLVAQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfX7mOKwnGf7fp-_T1Ypvbj0CUUg%3D%2F711x627%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAHYW5FF3ASRJLAB7Y6P77JLVAQ.gif&h=e050502b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上衣寫上反「國」安的區議員徐子見（左圖）被警方指涉非法集結拘捕（右圖）。&lt;br /&gt;許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/w0xQeBezrfeaMRhUK1dMtByuJ_I=/531x369/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L3KU5DCS3YG5BWF5NYO6QXJZHA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fw0xQeBezrfeaMRhUK1dMtByuJ_I%3D%2F531x369%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL3KU5DCS3YG5BWF5NYO6QXJZHA.gif&h=29f58a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被捕人士家屬昨晚到警署外守候。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_9s3zWY4aMS_3Id1z0fHDYGfbdQ=/531x369/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SBIINZDMWQ244UULUEADIWKKYI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_9s3zWY4aMS_3Id1z0fHDYGfbdQ%3D%2F531x369%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSBIINZDMWQ244UULUEADIWKKYI.gif&h=27fb35de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有防暴警失平衡跌倒，身旁同袍向記者及市民噴椒。何量鈞攝"},{"pid":"f5b735e822e73c220b19e630619a248391355896","tid":2083680,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T02:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HE0Php.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HE0Php.jpg&h=c5e5f272&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}